text.tspan: Blend Method, Opacity and Brush three
widgets are moved to Tool Options Panel
Creation Options: Circle Layer enable only,
Feather is set to Zero. When only one layer
type is enable, Link Origins is inactivated.
And Spline Origins at Center is activated only
when one (and more) of other five layer types
Creation Options: Circle and Outline Layer
enable. Feather is activated but is set to
Zero, so that Falloff is still inactivated.
